CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1953, page 23, reads: "Coffee, Doughnuts - A & P Food Stores special coffee promotion men. Charles Muehlman and George Holtman, made sure that everyone had a chance to taste A & P Coffee with Jane Parker Doughnuts."
TitMainTitle: Charles Muehlman and George Holtman, handing out samples of A & E coffee and Jane Parker doughnuts, for 1953 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Ammon Center
